Package: eventb-animate
Architecture: all
Depends: default-jre-headless | java-runtime-headless, ${misc:Depends}
Description: animate Event-B models with ProB
 eventb-animate animates Event-B models (.bum/.buc files, zip archives or Rodin
 project directories) using ProB, without a Rodin installation. It supports
 random animation, invariant checking, coverage, JSON trace save/replay, model
 visualisation and Event-B to classical B conversion.
 .
 The animator is a self-contained Java archive that bundles the ProB kernel and
 downloads the matching probcli on first use.
